<p>71. JAL 13/08/2012 Case no.: KHM 5/2012 State reply: None to date
 <b>Allegations of disruption by law enforcement officials of a human rights 
training course undertaken by two non-government organizations, and threats against 
</b></p>
<p><b>its members. 
