<p>392. JUA 19/11/2012 Case no.: SDN 8/2012 State reply: None to date
 <b>Alleged acts of intimidation against woman human rights defender as a result 
</b>of her cooperation with the African Commission on Human and People&#8217;s Rights.<b> 
