<p><b>  Tajikistan 
</b></p>
<p>411. JUA 29/08/2012 Case no.: TJK 3/2012  State reply: 16/10/2012
 <b>Allegations of lack of procedural safeguards in the case against the Association 
of Young Lawyers of Tajikistan (Amparo). 
