 <b>Alleged judicial and other harassment of activist.  
</b></p>
<p><b>  Observations 
</b></p>
<p>451. The Special Rapporteur regrets that, at the time of finalising the report, no response 
had been received to the communication sent during the reporting period. She considers the 
allegations received as serious and trusts that they will be duly investigated. </p>

<p><b>A/HRC/22/47/Add.4 
</b></p>
