<p><b>  Observations 
</b></p>
<p>455. The Special Rapporteur thanks the Government of Uzbekistan for the responses 
transmitted to her communications sent during the reporting period. Nonetheless, she 
remains gravely concerned at the situation of human rights defenders in Uzbekistan, 
particularly in light of reports of arbitrary arrests, physical attacks and ill-treatment of 
human rights defenders in detention. In this connection, the Special Rapporteur wishes to 
refer the Government of Uzbekistan to the provisions outlined in the Declaration on Human 
Rights Defenders, notably to article 2, article 5, point a), and article 12. 
</p>
